{
  "texts": [
    "In addition to the improved performance, we were able to examine the possibility of correcting the existing annotations with our GPT-based models.",
    "As mentioned earlier, we modified and used the open QA data set.",
    "Here, in addition to removing duplicates or deleting unanswered data, finding data with incorrect answers was based on the results of the GPT model (Fig. 5c).",
    "For example, there is an incorrect question-answer pair: the anode materials are not mentioned in the given context and 'nanomeshed' is mentioned as the cathode material; however, the annotated question is 'what is the anode material?",
    "', and the corresponding answer is 'nano-meshed'."
  ]
}